CE-NAM-5.0\t24334531\t23384098 (96.1%)\t19894719 (81.8%)\t17453243 (71.7%)\nMo17\troot\tH3K4me3\trep1\tZm-B73-REFERENCE-NAM-5.0\t38425670\t35438513 (92.2%)\t31304417 (81.5%)\t23395951 (60.9%)\nMo17\troot\tH3K4me3\trep2\tZm-B73-REFERENCE-NAM-5.0\t26294238\t23407683 (89.0%)\t20963716 (79.7%)\t16330220 (62.1%)\n", "name": "read_text_file", "tool_call_id": "call_TJRr6iXxwY0O6HMih6C3pGJQ"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_HGCM8lSVK3JUM19QYqQm1HJY", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. **Input Data**: Read `input/mapping_stats.tsv` which contains columns: Line, Tissue, Sample, Rep, Reference_genome, Total_reads, Passing_filtering, All_mapped_reads, Uniquely_mapped_reads.\\n2. **Data Transformation**:\\n   - Extract numeric values from columns formatted as `<count> (<pct>%)`.\\n   - Calculate Multi-mapping reads as `All_mapped_reads - Uniquely_mapped_reads`.\\n   - Calculate Unmapped reads as `Total_reads - All_mapped_reads`.\\n   - Calculate Filtered reads as `Total_reads - Passing_filtering`.\\n3. **Visualization**:\\n   - Create a two-panel PDF with stacked bar plots.\\n   - Each bar represents breakdown into Uniquely mapped, Multi-mapping, Unmapped, and Filtered reads.\\n   - Facet the plots by `Line`.\\n   - Title the plot `Mapping statistics for ChIP_demo samples`.\\n   - Set PDF dimensions to 10x12 inches, landscape.\\n4. **Output**: Save the PDF as `output/mapping_stats.pdf`.\\n5. **Validation**: Ensure the PDF is correctly formatted and saved in the output directory.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (985 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_HGCM8lSVK3JUM19QYqQm1HJY"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_bVYdwX3Dzfxp8tmdmD4EgSK7", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relative_path\": \"generate_mapping_stats.R\", \"content\": \"library(ggplot2)\\nlibrary(dplyr)\\nlibrary(tidyr)\\n\\n# Read the data\\ndata <- read.delim('input/mapping_stats.tsv', sep='\\\\t')\\n\\n# Extract numeric values from formatted columns\\ndata <- data %>%\\n  mutate(\\n    Passing_filtering = as.numeric(sub(' .*', '', Passing_filtering)),\\n    All_mapped_reads = as.numeric(sub(' .*', '', All_mapped_reads)),\\n    Uniquely_mapped_reads = as.numeric(sub(' .*', '', Uniquely_mapped_reads))\\n  )\\n\\n# Calculate additional columns\\ntransformed_data <- data %>%\\n  mutate(\\n    Multi_mapping_reads = All_mapped_reads - Uniquely_mapped_reads,\\n    Unmapped_reads = Total_reads - All_mapped_reads,\\n    Filtered_reads = Total_reads - Passing_filtering\\n  )\\n\\n# Prepare data for plotting\\nplot_data <- transformed_data %>%\\n  gather(key = \\\"Type\\\", value = \\\"Count\\\", Uniquely_mapped_reads, Multi_mapping_reads, Unmapped_reads, Filtered_reads)\\n\\n# Create the plot\\nplot <- ggplot(plot_data, aes(x = interaction(Tissue, Sample, Rep), y = Count, fill = Type)) +\\n  geom_bar(stat = \\\"identity\\\") +\\n  facet_wrap(~ Line) +\\n  theme_minimal() +\\n  labs(title = \\\"Mapping statistics for ChIP_demo samples\\\", x = \\\"Sample\\\", y = \\\"Read Count\\\") +\\n  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))\\n\\n# Save the plot\\npdf(\\\"output/mapping_stats.pdf\\\", width = 12, height = 10)\\nprint(plot)\\ndev.off()\\n\"}", "name": "write_text_file"}}]}], "hide_old_env_states": false, "hide_old_action_content": false}, "observation": [{"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (985 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_HGCM8lSVK3JUM19QYqQm1HJY"}], "next_observation": [{"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote 1283 bytes to generate_mapping_stats.R", "name": "write_text_file", "tool_call_id": "call_bVYdwX3Dzfxp8tmdmD4EgSK7"}], "action": {"call_id": {"run_id": "ec396400-7324-409a-837f-b6caff0a91cb", "fwd_id": "f1ef41f4-53a4-4c76-bce9-20e527106eef"}, "op_name": "_llm_call_op", "op_class_name": "ldp.graph.common